title: We All Share Our ‘What’s Wrong with People??!’ Stories + LoCash Stop By To Perform Their Hits + Lunchbox FINALLY Takes His Harry Potter Quiz
itunes:title: We All Share Our ‘What’s Wrong with People??!’ Stories + LoCash Stop By To Perform Their Hits + Lunchbox FINALLY Takes His Harry Potter Quiz
description:
We go around the room and share news stories that make us yell “WHAT’S WRONG WITH PEOPLE??” Our friends, LOCASH stop by to talk about their new project, living in two different states and they perform for us! Lunchbox finally takes his quiz on the 2nd Harry Potter movie!
